com.tinkerpop.frames.modules

Interface MethodHandler<T extends Annotation>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of annotation handled.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GremlinGroovyAnnotationHandler

    public interface MethodHandler<T extends Annotation>
    Allows handling of method on frames. Only the first method handler found is called. Instances of this class should be threadsafe.
